name: Gunslingers of the Sundew Crow
description: undefined, the Gunslingers of the Sundew Crow are renowned for their ability to nullify magic, and travel unseen even amidst extraordinary mages. Now, blessed with a sundew lotus due to their ties with the Groodu, they look towards the future with a glint in their eye. Their future is bright. The only question: what comes next?
